

     *************   /usr/ipsc/examples/rmfort_vx/vx287host/README   ***********


   This directory contains an example program designed to allow you to run
   a typical VX application using the iPSC Simulator.  You can build 
   one program in this directory:


	host.e - This host program shows how to call several of the veclib
	         routines. 


   Host.e can be made using the makefile.  To execute the application, type
   "host.e".  For more information, see the iPSC SIMULATOR USER'S GUIDE.
